thread.title: BRIEF-Omnicell Reports Q1 GAAP EPS Of $0.07

title: BRIEF-Omnicell Reports Q1 GAAP EPS Of $0.07
text:
April 26 (Reuters) - Omnicell Inc:
* OMNICELL ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER 2018 RESULTS * SEES Q2 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.36 TO $0.42
* Q1 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.29
* SEES Q2 2018 REVENUE $185 MILLION TO $190 MILLION * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.23 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 REVENUE $183 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $177.4 MILLION
* FOR YEAR 2018, COMPANY EXPECTS PRODUCT BOOKINGS TO BE BETWEEN $625 MILLION AND $660 MILLION
* FOR Q2 OF 2018, COMPANY EXPECTS NON-GAAP REVENUE TO BE BETWEEN $185 MILLION AND $190 MILLION
* COMPANY EXPECTS 2018 NON-GAAP REVENUE TO BE BETWEEN $780 MILLION AND $800 MILLION
* OMNICELL- SEES 2018 NON-GAAP REVENUE TO BE BETWEEN $780 MILLION AND $800 MILLION, AND NON-GAAP EARNINGS TO BE BETWEEN $1.85 AND $2.05 PER SHARE
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.97, REVENUE VIEW $790.3 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.97 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.42 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
